Package: ggrefine
Title: Refined ggplot2 Themes
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("David", "Hodge", , "davidhodge931@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3868-7501"))
Description: A set of complete ggplot2 themes and theme polish functions.
    Themes control the overall look, while polish functions let you selectively 
    remove gridlines, axis lines, and ticks based on the focus and type of each
    axis.
